Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从小径上过来时我就闻到了花香\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could smell the flowers when you came down the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼拜堂已经空置多年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This chapel has stood empty for years. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有传言说有人躲在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are rumours that someone is hiding there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在躲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信魔法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you believe in magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个巫师对她施了咒语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An enchanter has cast a spell on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她在睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...that's why she's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能叫醒她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't you wake her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要时间帮她醒过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need time to help wake her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你帮我拦住外人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to help me keep the people away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  太感谢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保护好她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep her safe, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数千年来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For many millennia,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,权威者统治着天堂王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Authority has ruled in the Kingdom of Heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制着一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with absolute control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自诩为创世主  天父  全能的神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He named himself the Creator, the Father, the Almighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是一派胡言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is none of those
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他与我们一样  只是天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but just an angel like ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个黑暗天使在旁辅佐他的统治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he rules with a dark angel by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为真相而战  却被从天堂驱逐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We, who fought for truth, were cast out of the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此后  我们在世界之间穿梭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since then, we have lived between the worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观察  伺机复仇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}watching and waiting for vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:01:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类中间迸发出了希望的火苗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A spark of hope is alive among humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位大胆的领袖在召集勇士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A bold leader is rallying warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他虽是凡人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He may be mortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他的野心超越了同类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but his ambitions transcend his kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条毒蛇受到了召唤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A serpent has been summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个新夏娃出现了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A new Eve emerges.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的反叛时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The time for a new rebellion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将来临\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找一个女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm looking for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中等身高  黑发  棕色的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Medium height, dark hair, brown eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫莱拉  她的精灵叫潘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her name's Lyra. She has a daemon called Pan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰  是你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger! Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你  帮帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  加把劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For goodness' sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行器可能还没准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The craft may not be ready for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就得怪我们俩了  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then that is on the pair of us, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清空思绪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clear your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后振荡器坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've lost the rear oscillator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不喝药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't drink your medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎么能好起来呢  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how will you get better, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你们怎么...  -我们不会伤害你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How did you-- - We're not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bene Elim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你们的语言说就是天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Angels, in your language.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以人形与你见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We come to you in human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Angels?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是想谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We just want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟着我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊萨哈特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}AEsahaettr.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行器应该是摔烂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think the craft is pretty much done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们要怎么回共和国去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how will we get back to the Republic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们总会有办法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be able to figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有发现吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前路安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like the path is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥官  我们去救人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander, let's go get our man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We secure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-安全 -安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Clear! - Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥滚威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ogunwe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一位是奥滚威指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which one of you is Commander Ogunwe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的小朋友是什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you, and your little friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是阿斯里尔·贝拉克瓦勋爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am Lord Asriel Belacqua.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我意图进军天堂王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I intend to march upon the Kingdom of Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很希望你可以加入我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I should very much like you to join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说过你的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've heard stories about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚跟教廷宣了战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have just made war with the Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己去打吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll let you fight that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听听他要说的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我的朋友并不来自你的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My friends and I, we are not from your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们对你们的教廷没什么兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have little interest in your Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为你而来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We came here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起抵抗权威者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Join with me in my fight against the Authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我们有共同的立场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I know that we stand for the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你有多少手下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know the number you command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要你的军队  但我需要你做领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want your army, but I need your leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来  加入最终的胜利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me. Be a part of the final victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来日内瓦  麦克菲尔主教\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to Geneva, Cardinal MacPhail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庭长神父  有请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father President, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庭长神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father President.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我说说逮捕的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me of this arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在现场发现了这玩意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We recovered this material from the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它被当着众人背诵出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was recited before an audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人听得如痴如醉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}many inebriated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后还进行了激烈讨论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and followed by feverish discussion,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和怪诞的思想交流\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a grotesque exchange of ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰罗姆神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father Jerome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think should be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应以异端邪说的罪名将作者监禁起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The author must be imprisoned for heresy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海斯特神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father Heyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整栋楼里还藏了数十本这样的书\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were dozens more like it hidden throughout the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有出席者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All attendees imprisoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和所有持有作者著作的人都被监禁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as well as anyone found in possession of the author's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-戈梅兹  -戈梅兹神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Gomez. - Father Gomez.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是我  你会怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you were in my position, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉体赎罪  当众进行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Physical atonement... in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被诉持有此书的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For those charged with possession,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或许会选择鞭刑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd choose, perhaps, the whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于作者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the author,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,采取能留下更持久伤痕的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something which leaves a little more... lasting damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐惧是馈赠  能让人长进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fear is a gift. It allows people to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会把我们杀鸡儆猴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll make examples of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴鲁克  我们没时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Baruch, we do not have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要那把刀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need that knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你们别跟着我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you to stop following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是怎么穿梭世界的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can you cut through worlds?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是由尘埃构成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are made of Dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以穿过空中无形的空间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and can pass through invisible spaces in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是通往其他世界的门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}gateways into other worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看得到  但你看不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can see them, but you cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔塞莫斯和我一直在寻找伊萨哈特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Balthamos and I have been searching for AEsahaettr...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一场大战即将来临\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because there is a great war coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有有意识的生灵已经卷入了大战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All conscious beings are engaged in a battle already,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是每个人都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}though not all of us know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的力量每分每秒都在强大起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The enemy's power is growing stronger every minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你就持有能让我们获胜的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you have the weapon that will enable us to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得跟我们去找阿斯里尔勋爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must come with us to Lord Asriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在召集军队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gathering an army
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-意图...  -我知道他是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- with the purpose to-- - I know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人跟我说过他  他的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone told me about him. About all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The war,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及我要拿着它  跟阿斯里尔并肩作战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how I'm supposed to fight alongside Asriel, with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能跟你们走  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't go with you. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找我的朋友  莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm looking for my friend, Lyra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯里尔的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Asriel's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他不会在乎  但她失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not that he cares, but she's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她需要我的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She needs my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀的重要性远超乎你的想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That knife is more important than you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是你不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉才是现在对我最重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra's the most important thing to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你要马上跟我们走  -不然呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You will come with us now-- - Or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你朋友的事我很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry about your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出她对你来说很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can see she means a lot to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她遭遇了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们遭到了袭击  她被抓走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were attacked. She was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谁抓了她  -我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- By who? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撇下她先走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went ahead without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为她不会有事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought she would be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我回来时  她就不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I came back, she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管阿斯里尔需要什么  让他等着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever Asriel wants, he can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我们会一直跟着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You do realize we're just going to keep following you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你回心转意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们就继续跟着我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you can keep following me because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次我穿越后  你们都找到了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've managed to find me every time I've cut through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀  它吸引尘埃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The knife. It attracts Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有人类不具备的感知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have senses that humans do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们能找到我  就能找到莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you can find me, you can find Lyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我去找她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take me to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  我就跟你们去找阿斯里尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, I will come with you to Asriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do not have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴鲁克  他们要不了多久就会找到我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will not take them long, Baruch. They will find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we will be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔塞莫斯  我们没别的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Balthamos, we don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是莱拉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was Lyra's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说它跟刀是一个原理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She says it's powered the same way as the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.58,0:22:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你可以用它找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you can use it to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是由尘埃驱动的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's powered by Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要点时间  但我们会找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will need a little time, but we will find her,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管她在哪个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whatever world she is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉  我在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra, I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰  这是什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger, what is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:22:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:22:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马琪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Machi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  我好想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God, I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心肝  看看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my sweet. Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长高了15厘米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've grown six inches,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快跟我一般高了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're almost as tall as me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.74,0:24:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸还有工作  我就回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daddy has work to do. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.14,0:24:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你女儿真可爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a beautiful little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.14,0:24:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多久没见着她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long since you last saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.94,0:24:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十个月零16天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ten months and 16 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.70,0:24:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来没有可能能离开那监牢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had no hope of leaving that cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.74,0:24:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你和你的猫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until you and your cat
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.62,0:24:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑来招募我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}came to recruit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.46,0:24:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.58,0:24:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在考虑你到底是疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trying to decide if you're a madman...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.22,0:24:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是天才\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.10,0:25:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒希望两者可以共存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I rather hoped the two could coexist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.98,0:25:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯里尔徐勋爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, Lord Asriel...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.22,0:25:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你的战争究竟是针对谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tell me who your war is really against,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.06,0:25:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你想要我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and what you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.54,0:25:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要向权威者发起挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My fight is with the Authority himself--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.90,0:25:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过了  但这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said that before, but it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.62,0:25:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类不能反抗创世主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Humankind cannot stand against its Creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.98,0:25:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他逼我们在他脚边下跪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he forces us to kneel at his feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.14,0:25:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他并不是创世主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he is not the Creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.86,0:25:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.46,0:25:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.50,0:25:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-天使  -仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- An angel? - Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.82,0:25:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是怎么知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how do you know all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.42,0:25:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便这是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...even if it were true?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.86,0:25:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几千年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some millennia ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.46,0:25:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个天使发现了权威者的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}another angel discovered the Authority's secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.30,0:25:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个天使  泽法妮娅  现在是我的理事会成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, that angel, Xaphania, sits on my council.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.78,0:25:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥滚威  我在召集各个世界的最强大的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ogunwe, I am gathering the greatest from every world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.94,0:25:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括天堂的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From even the heavens above,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.90,0:25:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想请你来帮我掀起战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I want you to help me wage my war.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.50,0:26:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该感到受宠若惊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should be flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.38,0:26:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是远道而来  这就对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I have come rather a long way, so yes, you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.98,0:26:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯里尔勋爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lord Asriel...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.86,0:26:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.18,0:26:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马琪是我的最小的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Machi is my youngest daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.46,0:26:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还有一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I have another.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.62,0:26:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教廷早就盯上了我们的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Temple have been targeting our children for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.06,0:26:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但近年来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But in recent years...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.74,0:26:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们抓走了孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they began taking them away...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.94,0:26:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行训练\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for training.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.42,0:26:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿丽娅是教廷的财产\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aria... is the property of the Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.10,0:26:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她看来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To her...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.90,0:27:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.78,0:27:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只认权威者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is only the Authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.74,0:27:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所认识的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the girl I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.46,0:27:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.42,0:27:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她仍是我的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But she's still my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.30,0:27:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你提出的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand what you offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.54,0:27:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还要打自己的仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I have my own battles here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.30,0:27:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有义务尽我所能  拯救更多人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And an obligation to save as many sons...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.78,0:27:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿子和女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and daughters as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.34,0:27:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以吗  拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.66,0:28:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过这种情况  她的精灵被切割了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen this before. Her daemon has been severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.78,0:28:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她才不是邪魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is not demonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.14,0:28:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那个意思  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not say she was. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.74,0:28:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  请允许我解释  斯特尔玛丽娅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, if you'll allow me to explain. Stelmaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.46,0:28:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔玛丽娅和我是一体的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stelmaria and I are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.02,0:28:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我的精灵  我的灵魂  也可以这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is my daemon. My soul, if you use that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.90,0:28:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿丽娅的精灵原本在她体内\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aria's daemon resided within.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.34,0:28:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和精灵之间的纽带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The link that binds us to our daemon
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.42,0:28:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常强大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is immensely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.18,0:28:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一旦它被切断  便所剩无几\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when it is severed, well, very little remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.62,0:28:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在夺走我们的灵魂  奥滚威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are taking our souls, Ogunwe,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.90,0:28:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也带走了我们的人性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and with them our humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.98,0:28:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样更好控制我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To make us easier to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.78,0:28:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把我们变成这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To make us this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.34,0:28:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无人机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drones.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.42,0:29:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把马琪带回来  所有人进屋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get Machi on the ground! Everyone, inside now!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.38,0:29:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开火  他们想引我们出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold your fire. They're trying to draw us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.14,0:29:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您找我  庭长神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sent for me, Father President?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.02,0:29:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进  戈梅兹神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in, Father Gomez.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.66,0:29:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来日内瓦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have come to Geneva
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.34,0:29:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为一件要事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on a matter of great significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.38,0:29:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗拉·帕维尔的真理仪让我得知了一则预言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fra Pavel's alethiometer has informed me of a prophecy
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.30,0:30:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真的  我也相信它是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which, if true, a-- and I believe it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.98,0:30:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么它或能让我们堕入黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}risks plunging us into a darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.90,0:30:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是世界前所未见的黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the like of which the world has not experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.54,0:30:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时此刻  世上有一个女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a girl wandering the earth at this very moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.70,0:30:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是夏娃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she is Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.10,0:30:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所有人的母亲  一切罪孽的起源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mother of us all, and the cause of all sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.86,0:30:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理仪说  如果这个孩子被毒蛇诱惑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The instrument says that if this child is tempted by the serpent,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.66,0:30:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很可能会堕落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she will likely fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.22,0:30:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦她堕落  罪孽和尘埃就赢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if she does fall, then sin and Dust will triumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.86,0:30:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这绝不能发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This cannot happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.02,0:30:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就阻止她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, we stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.46,0:30:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.54,0:30:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  我们只能等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately, we are at the mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.30,0:30:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理仪和解读者怎么说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the instrument and its user.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.14,0:30:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗拉·帕维尔的进展出奇的慢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fra Pavel's work is unbearably slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.38,0:30:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他找到这孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When he does locate the child...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.46,0:31:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就派兵去把她抓回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we will send troops to retrieve her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.54,0:31:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想请你  戈梅兹神父  去带队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I would like you, Father Gomez... to lead them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.18,0:31:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would be an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.74,0:31:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以去见见弗拉·帕维尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could perhaps drop in on Fra Pavel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.94,0:31:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看能不能让他快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See if I can speed him up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.86,0:31:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.58,0:31:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多人在找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All these men after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.86,0:31:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了  这不会变的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tell you, it'll never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.26,0:32:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上有些力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are forces out there
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.34,0:32:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本无法理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you can't begin to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.54,0:32:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是别那么看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you wouldn't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.26,0:32:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你不希望我保护她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you rather I didn't keep her safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.38,0:32:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在囚禁她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're keeping her prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.18,0:32:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.42,0:32:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Afraid I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.82,0:33:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.26,0:33:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.94,0:33:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是在精灵世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is in the world of the daemons.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.06,0:33:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.26,0:33:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跟一个女人在一起  那女人强行控制着她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's with a woman who is holding her against her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.98,0:33:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们在一座岩洞屋里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a house carved into the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.14,0:33:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里位于北海上的一座偏远岛屿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's on a remote island in the German ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.94,0:33:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要乘船去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will need passage on a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.86,0:33:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但莱拉没受伤吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Lyra's not harmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.50,0:34:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  只是在睡觉和做梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Just asleep and dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.22,0:34:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以跟我说说那女人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can you tell me about the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.34,0:34:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的精灵是只金猴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her daemon is a golden monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.06,0:34:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是她妈妈  -她妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Her mother. - Her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.50,0:34:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉如果跟她母亲在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra's mother's the worst possible person
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.26,0:34:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太糟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she could be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.74,0:34:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔塞莫斯会带你去找她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Balthamos will take you to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.38,0:34:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去找阿斯里尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I must go to Asriel
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.42,0:34:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他你和伊萨哈特的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and tell him about you and AEsahaettr.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.94,0:34:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定这样安全吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure this is safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.90,0:34:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接去找莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go straight to Lyra,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.94,0:34:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很快就将重聚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we will be together again before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.10,0:34:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不记得我答应要陪着这男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not remember agreeing to accompany the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.58,0:34:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟紧威尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay close to Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.50,0:34:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等孩子们重聚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As soon as the children are reunited,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.30,0:34:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一起来阿斯里尔的共和国找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you will both come to me in Asriel's Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.22,0:35:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庭长神父麦克菲尔派我来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father President MacPhail sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.42,0:35:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.22,0:35:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快找到了  神父  我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am close, Father. I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.78,0:35:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这任务对你来说是个重担\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see this task has weighed heavily on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.54,0:35:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此压力  如此重大的责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The pressure. Such great responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.86,0:36:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定让你头脑很不清醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It must muddle the mind terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.38,0:36:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是解读的最后部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is this... ...final part of the reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.34,0:36:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Its... meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.78,0:36:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是搞不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...eludes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.14,0:36:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是需要更多时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just need a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.02,0:36:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能做我们能做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can only do that of which we are capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.26,0:36:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庭长神父建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father President has advised
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.50,0:36:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果读不出坐标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that if the coordinates are not forthcoming,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.26,0:36:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么或许现在需要  重新教育你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then perhaps, the time has come to re-educate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.58,0:36:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.58,0:36:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我能找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I will find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.46,0:36:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.46,0:36:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我毫不怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no doubt that you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.38,0:37:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉  求你  醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra. Wake up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.18,0:37:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.46,0:37:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以逃走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.94,0:38:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.06,0:38:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.22,0:38:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跑不掉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.82,0:38:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们总得试试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.58,0:38:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲在这里  或许会有人看到我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hide here. Maybe someone will see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.54,0:38:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.98,0:39:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.70,0:39:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.42,0:39:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.70,0:39:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.28,0:39:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉  你在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.30,0:39:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总能让我惊奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never cease to amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.58,0:39:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.22,0:40:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你为什么要这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do understand why you're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.58,0:40:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样跟我在一起感觉很奇怪吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must be strange being here, like this... with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.58,0:40:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我带你来这里  不是为了关着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I haven't brought you here to keep you jailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.58,0:40:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done it to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.02,0:40:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lyra, darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.22,0:40:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要来抓你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there are people coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.22,0:40:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dangerous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.66,0:40:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're so brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.50,0:40:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇气十足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So courageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.10,0:40:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你不会相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you won't believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.14,0:41:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我这是为了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I... I am doing this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.42,0:41:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  亲爱的  来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, darling, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.54,0:41:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你在一起绝不会安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will never be safe with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.70,0:41:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.78,0:41:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.02,0:41:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥官  他们去矿山了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander, they're heading for the mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.10,0:41:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会跟我们拉开四英里距离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They will miss us by four miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.66,0:41:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  我们躲到天黑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. We'll stay covered until sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.62,0:41:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力反抗  指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Putting up a good fight, Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.05,0:41:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的战役太小了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the battle you're engaged in is too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.50,0:41:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便你赢得了对教廷的战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if you win this fight against the Temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.98,0:41:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,权威者只会派来更多仆从替代他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Authority will send more servants in their place
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.46,0:41:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼你再次下跪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to put you back on your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.66,0:41:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们每个世界都有  我见识到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are in every world. I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.46,0:42:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总说什么其他世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You keep talkin' of other worlds
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.26,0:42:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像指望我会相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as if you expect me to believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.90,0:42:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.58,0:42:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是众多世界中的一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is but one world among many.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.94,0:42:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个世界里都在发生一样的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In every single one of them, the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.90,0:42:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子被残害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Children, mutilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.50,0:42:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学  学习  被视为罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Science, learning, criminalized,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.23,0:42:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个文明在天空下瑟瑟发抖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and whole civilizations cowering under the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.34,0:42:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾像你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was like you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.78,0:42:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的世界  我们的教廷叫教会当局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In my world, the Temple, they are called the Magisterium
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.22,0:42:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大半辈子都浪费在跟他们作战上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I have wasted most of my life fighting them
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.58,0:42:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我发现  他们不过是权威者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until I discovered that they were but one arm
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.38,0:42:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量的一根手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the Authority's might,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.86,0:42:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那只野兽有无数手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that beast has countless arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.54,0:42:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一值得你赌上孩子们的性命的战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only fight worth risking your children's lives for
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.16,0:42:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在别的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}lies elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.86,0:42:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这地上的共和国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Republic, down here in the good Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.62,0:42:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反抗他天上的王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}against his Kingdom up there in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.78,0:42:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是唯一获得胜利的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is the only way to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.34,0:42:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们砍掉野兽的头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We cut off the head of the beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.54,0:42:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的便会分崩离析\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the rest will crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.90,0:42:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.72,0:42:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.82,0:42:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我相信的事太难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you ask me to believe is too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.86,0:42:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不容易接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a lot to take in...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.38,0:43:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我带你看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so, let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.18,0:43:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.18,0:43:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就可以自己决定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that way you can decide for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.62,0:43:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你去别的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me take you to another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.10,0:43:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.58,0:43:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别烦我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just let me be.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.42,0:44:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想到办法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.14,0:44:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为他早该到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just thought he'd be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.10,0:44:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你知道她是怎么读的吗  -不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you know how she reads it? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.46,0:44:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些真理仪的解读者通常要学习很多年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Readers of those instruments have normally studied many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.18,0:44:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此  他们也需要书籍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even then, they can only understand
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.42,0:44:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-才能进行解读  -她不是在瞎说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- with the help of books. - She wasn't making it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.34,0:44:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许她很会...编\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps she's a very... skilled inventor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.86,0:44:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会解读\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She can read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.82,0:44:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它让她知道了她根本不可能知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It told her things she could have never known,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.54,0:44:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如我父亲在哪  这是她的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like where my father was. It's a part of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.78,0:44:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像刀是我的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just like the knife's a part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.98,0:44:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们在找的港口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the port we're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.10,0:44:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只需要找艘船了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, we just need a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.18,0:45:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是尤雷科·伯尔尼松国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am King Iorek Byrnison.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.90,0:45:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们困住了我的一头熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've trapped one of my bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.78,0:45:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上放了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Release her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.26,0:45:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能认识那只熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I know that bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.98,0:45:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我可以跟他谈谈  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can talk to him. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.54,0:45:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是莱拉的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Lyra's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.98,0:45:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.06,0:45:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.22,0:45:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.30,0:45:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.74,0:46:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-让开  小子  -你得停下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get out of my way, child. - You have to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.94,0:46:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还有无辜者呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are innocent people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.94,0:46:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们抓了一头我的熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have taken one of my bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.26,0:46:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.98,0:46:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一对一地跟你决斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to fight you. In single combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.74,0:46:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢了  你就放过这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I win, you leave these people alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.86,0:46:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.20,0:46:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以随意处置他们和我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do whatever you want with them, and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.38,0:46:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要跟我决斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wish to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.10,0:46:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你决斗是可耻的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would be shameful to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.14,0:46:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如一只离壳的牡蛎一般脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are as weak as an oyster out of its shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.42,0:46:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们让决斗公平点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's make it a fair fight, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.98,0:46:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有盔甲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have all the armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.90,0:46:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have none.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.34,0:46:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.74,0:46:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.02,0:46:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就更势均力敌了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be better matched then, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.02,0:46:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你在做什么吗  小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what you are doing, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.94,0:47:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空铁  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sky-iron, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.30,0:47:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚不可摧  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Impenetrable, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.62,0:47:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.30,0:47:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我还是得不戴盔甲跟你决斗了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess I have to fight you without armor after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.30,0:47:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打不过那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot fight that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.10,0:47:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把刀太奇怪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That knife is too strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.86,0:47:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赢了  小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You win, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.22,0:47:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上放了那头熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Free that bear, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.18,0:47:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们听到了  快去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You heard the boy. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.58,0:47:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么  小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is your name, child?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.78,0:48:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔·佩里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will Parry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.14,0:48:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔·佩里  你在找莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, Will Parry, you're looking for Lyra?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.94,0:48:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跟她母亲在一起  被她囚禁着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's with her mother, being held against her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.42,0:48:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们得去救她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we must go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.38,0:48:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庭长神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father President.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.22,0:48:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去见了弗拉·帕维尔好几次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I visited Fra Pavel. Several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.50,0:48:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I helped him to...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.78,0:48:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}focus his mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.06,0:48:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中了精神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.46,0:48:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已判断出  那孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has since divined that the child
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.50,0:48:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正跟她妈妈在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is with her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.62,0:48:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.50,0:48:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了这个情报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With this information,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.26,0:48:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信我能找到那女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am confident I can locate the girl myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.26,0:49:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我需要使用没有得到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I will need to use methods that aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.70,0:49:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,官方准许的手段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}officially sanctioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.86,0:49:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要做什么就去做吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must do whatever you need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.06,0:49:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦你知道了她们的方位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The second you have their position,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.90,0:49:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去找她们  抓到那孩子和她妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}go to them, get the child, get the mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.02,0:49:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她们直接带回来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and bring them directly to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.46,0:49:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽莎·库尔特是毒妇  擅长摆弄人心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marisa Coulter is evil, she is persuasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.30,0:49:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别信任她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.82,0:49:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神父  我成年之后  每一天都在预忏悔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father, I've done pre-emptive penance every day of my adult life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.74,0:49:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会不惜一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will do whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.50,0:49:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她们抓回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is required to get them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.14,0:49:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对权威者的忠心不会白费\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your dedication to the Authority will not go unappreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.02,0:51:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯里尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Asriel,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.90,0:51:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你不是在要我去送死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do hope you're not walking me to my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.94,0:51:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡是谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And death is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.90,0:51:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了  死亡是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're wrong. Death is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.10,0:51:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见识过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.14,0:51:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无数战争中见过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than my fair share of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.66,0:51:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥官  权威者不知怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander, somehow the Authority
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.46,0:51:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭曲了尘埃的自然秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has managed to pervert the natural order of Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.02,0:51:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道他怎么做到的  但等我查清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know how but when I find out,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.18,0:52:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  死亡就会死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}believe me, death is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.22,0:52:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我听的够多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe I've heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.94,0:52:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会看到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.82,0:52:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔玛利娅  听我令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stelmaria, on my mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.42,0:52:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...I want you to bite down.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.06,0:52:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.90,0:52:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三  二  一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.10,0:52:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.66,0:52:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到天堂共和国  指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to the Republic of Heaven, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.70,0:52:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是召集军队吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd gather my people if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.58,0:52:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的战争要开始了  我们必须赢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The real war is coming, and we must win it.


